name: [Deep Freeze] Iceman
desc: The youngest original member of the X-Men, Iceman has also been part of other mutant and hero alliances including X-Factor, the Defenders, and the Champions of Los Angeles. His powers have grown over the years and he is now considered one of the more powerful mutants currently active.
effect: Notably intensify ATK of your Speed Cards.

name: [Spring Forward] Box Hiding the Power of the Green Super Hero
name_id: [Spring Forward] Box Hiding the Power of the Green Super Hero
desc: It's spring! Things are growing... and turning green...

name: [Deep Freeze] Iceman+
desc: My powers keep increasing. I keep discovering new things I can do. Even I don't know how much stronger I'm going to get. Even Xavier doesn't know. The sky's the limit... or maybe I should say the limit is absolute zero.
effect: Notably intensify ATK of your Speed Cards.

name: [Gotcha!] Goblin-in-the-Box
desc: There once was an agent of S.H.I.E.L.D. / Who asked that this card be revealed / You thought it was Hulk / But I fooled you—don't sulk! / You can get your revenge in the field!
effect: Remarkably degrade ATK of all of opponent's Cards.
